Scotland will be the subject of travel photographer and lecturer Mort Loveman 
from 1 to 2:30 p.m. on Thursday at Roxbury Community Center, Roxbury Memorial 
Park, 471 S. Roxbury Drive, Beverly Hills. Admission free. For more 
information, call (213) 550-4761. 
